<!DOCTYPE html> <html lang="mn"> <head> <meta charset="UTF-8"> <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"> <title>Week 2 - Creative</title> <style> body { margin: 0; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background: #0f172a; color: white; overflow-x: hidden; } /* HERO */ .hero { height: 100vh; display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center; align-items: center; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0f172a, #1e3a8a, #7c3aed); text-align: center; } .hero h1 { font-size: 60px; margin: 0; } .hero p { opacity: 0.7; } /* SECTION */ .section { padding: 100px 20px; display: flex; justify-content: center; } .card { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05); backdrop-filter: blur(10px); padding: 40px; border-radius: 20px; max-width: 800px; width: 100%; transform: translateY(50px); opacity: 0; transition: all 0.6s ease; } .card.show { transform: translateY(0); opacity: 1; } /* TITLE */ .title { font-size: 32px; margin-bottom: 20px; } /* LIST */ ul { line-height: 1.8; } /* CURSOR GLOW */ .cursor { position: fixed; width: 20px; height: 20px; background: radial-gradient(circle, #3b82f6, transparent); border-radius: 50%; pointer-events: none; transform: translate(-50%, -50%); } </style> </head> <body> <div class="cursor" id="cursor"></div> <!-- HERO --> <section class="hero"> <h1>WEEK 2</h1> <p>Салбарын ерөнхий мэдлэг</p> </section> <!-- INDUSTRY --> <section class="section"> <div class="card"> <div class="title">📦 Industry Knowledge</div> <ul> <li>Логистикийн үндэс ойлголт</li> <li>Олон улсын тээвэр</li> <li>Supply chain урсгал</li> </ul> </div> </section> <!-- BUSINESS --> <section class="section"> <div class="card"> <div class="title">💼 Business Knowledge</div> <ul> <li>Why – Асуудал</li> <li>Who – Зорилтот хэрэглэгч</li> <li>What – Шийдэл</li> <li>How – Хэрэгжүүлэх</li> </ul> </div> </section> <!-- GROWTH --> <section class="section"> <div class="card"> <div class="title">📈 Personal Growth</div> <ul> <li>Цаг хугацааны үнэ цэнэ</li> <li>Анхаарал төвлөрөл</li> <li>Өсөлтийн mindset</li> </ul> </div> </section> <script> /* SCROLL ANIMATION */ const cards = document.querySelectorAll('.card'); window.addEventListener('scroll', () => { cards.forEach(card => { const top = card.getBoundingClientRect().top; if(top < window.innerHeight - 100){ card.classList.add('show'); } }); }); /* CURSOR EFFECT */ const cursor = document.getElementById('cursor'); document.addEventListener('mousemove', e => { cursor.style.left = e.clientX + 'px'; cursor.style.top = e.clientY + 'px'; }); </script> </body> </html>
